title: Dr.Slender Episode 1 Escape v1.4
description:
Survival horror, inspired by the character Slenderman
Enter Chris Arknikelle skin, and tries to escape from the asylum of Dr.Slender
You will search for 4 Documents to escape.

Find the keys and objects needed to emerge unscathed from the asylum.
Be careful with the spirits, you can kill with just fuck you.

Looking kits help as some enemies will hit you on your adventure.
Hide the Dr.Slender since it will follow you anywhere.

What's New:

1) Now available in English
2) we have released a monster called celder, is located in the first sector, be careful
3) 3) Gusanus (enemy on the second floor) now has less speed, so will have some time to review
this room
4) New test control divided into 2 parts of the screen
